Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,228)}感到不安的話馬上和我們打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1185,219)}免費諮詢
