Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1233,646)}憑此廣告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202,670)}偵探委託費零元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.82,NoteLesser,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,694)}婚外戀調查費零元
